	<h1> <a href="/"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/E4cqzO9.png"></a> || <a href="/posts"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/QDfVXp1.png"></a> ||
    <a href="/users"><img src="http://i.imgur.com/LlDmtZR.png"></a> ||
